@page
@model ManualModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Process Manual";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    Detailed Registration Process Manual

    Initiate Registration

    Navigate to the "Nordic Nest" homepage.
    Locate and click on the 'Register' button, typically found at the top right corner of the page.
    Enter Registration Details

    A registration form will appear prompting you to enter your personal details.
    Fill in the following fields:
    Username: Choose a unique username for your account.
    Password: Enter a strong password. For enhanced security, use a mix of letters, numbers, and special characters.
    Email Address: Provide a valid email address. This will be used for account verification and communication.
    Email Verification Process

    After submitting the registration form, check your email inbox for a verification message from "Nordic Nest".
    If you see an error indicating the email is already used, you'll need to try another email address.
    Click the verification link within the email to activate your account.
    Account Verification Confirmation

    Upon clicking the verification link, you'll be redirected to a confirmation page indicating successful account activation.
    Here, you may be prompted to log in with your new credentials to confirm they are working correctly.
    Finalizing Account Setup

    After logging in for the first time, you may be taken through additional setup steps. This could include providing more detailed personal and financial information.
    You might be asked to set up security questions, link a bank account, or set financial goals.
    Welcome to "Nordic Nest"

    Once the registration process is complete, you'll be welcomed to your personal dashboard.
    Take some time to familiarize yourself with the dashboard features and settings.
    Start Using Financial Tools

    Begin by creating jobs or income streams and setting up savings goals.
    Follow guided steps to manage savings accounts, track loans, and establish a budget tailored to your financial situation.
    Support and Assistance

    If at any point you run into difficulties, "Nordic Nest" provides a customer support service. Look for a 'Help' or 'Support' link, often located in the website footer or dashboard area.
    Detailed Login Process Manual

    Accessing Login Page

    From the "Nordic Nest" homepage, identify the 'Login' button. Click to open the login form.
    Entering Login Credentials

    In the login form, enter your username and the password you set during registration.
    Ensure the accuracy of the details to prevent any login errors.
    Successful Login

    After entering your credentials, press the 'Login' button.
    You should be redirected to your personal "Nordic Nest" dashboard where you can access all features.
    Troubleshooting Login Issues

    If you cannot log in, ensure there are no typos in your username and password and that Caps Lock is off.
    If multiple attempts fail, use the 'Forgot Password' link to reset your password, following the on-screen instructions.
    Resetting Your Password

    To reset your password, you'll typically need to provide your registered email address.
    You'll receive an email with a link to create a new password. Follow the link and the instructions carefully.
    Final Steps

    Once logged in, review any notifications or alerts that may be waiting for you on the dashboard.
    If you've logged in after a period of inactivity, check for any updates or changes to the platform that may have occurred.
    Security Reminder

    Remember to log out of your account after each session if you're on a shared or public computer to protect your personal financial data.
    Need Help?

    If you're experiencing persistent issues or have any questions, reach out to "Nordic Nest" customer support via the contact methods provided on the website.
</p>
